  "text": "A Multi-Dilation (MD) module is then used to obtain the crack features of multiple context sizes. The dilated convolution [CITATION_1] can increase the context and learn deeper features without compromising the edge resolution. It is employed in the MD module with multiple rates to extract the crack MD features of multiple context sizes. With the proposed MD module, the cracks of different widths and topologies can be robustly detected.",
